{"tid":1543133,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"平行時空嘅C9 Feat.我老母","createTime":"2019-09-05T05:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T07:55:08.000Z","uid":207439,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d6055b45ec8142a1f2208da7449f840cb8eb2418","tid":1543133,"uid":207439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:35:16.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小女係頻繁有去發夢嘅，而我媽媽係淺藍嘅C9。 <br />\n日日十點我都有係窗到嗌，我媽媽都會阻止我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日佢啲C9朋友都黎左。佢地要出去行街街，小女就開左<a href=\"https://t.me/hkmaplive \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkmaplive%20&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=1a644d31\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkmaplive </a>幫佢地睇睇有無狗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />媽媽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />C9朋友<br />\n<br />\n我：宜家柴灣有狗喎，你地知咩係狗架何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n媽媽：唔好咁話人地啦，人地都係打份工啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nC9朋友：咪係囉，唔好咁話人啦。<br />\n<br />\n我（嗌）：唔會囉。狗都要死，我見到就要打鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n媽媽、C9: 唔好咁啦，唔好打佢地，有啲都係好人尼。<br />\n<br />\n我：係好人一早唔撚做啦，六月Quit左啦。所有狗都要死！<br />\n<br />\n之後我就不停Loop<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以，我要打撚死啲狗。<br />\n一拳一拳咁打撚死佢地！打撚死佢地！</span></div></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就Dead-air左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 日日屌鳩媽子廢老 有日仲同我講外國勢力<br />\n估唔到C9們到今時今日都覺得狗係打份工仲要有良知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1feed72fac69e2d782e6327ecbe20337f5fc261d","tid":1543133,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:35:27.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyFk4T.jpg&h=2bffae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsV05wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsV05wz.jpg&h=d54e941c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUH604U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUH604U.jpg&h=74590733&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a45549543ea8964c44a61e4ed7bfbd80c1769e6","tid":154313